## <a id="limitations"></a>Limitations

<p>The DataStax Enterprise for PCF (Beta) has the following limitations:</p>

<ul>
<li>It is for development purpose only.  Users will not receive general support from DataStax if their DataStax Entrprise clusters are provisioned using the DataStax Enterprise for PCF (Beta) during the beta period.</li>
<li>The provisioned DataStax Enterprise (DSE) clusters do not provide DSE Search, DSE Analytics and DSE Graph features.</li>
<li>Developers are limited to three different service plans.</li>
<li>The DataStax Enterprise for PCF tile can be installed in a multi-AZs PCF environments.  However, it can only provision DataStax Enterprise cluster nodes in a single AZ domain.</li>
<li>Maximum DataStax Enterprise cluster size is 40.</li>
</ul>

